null},{"id":39861723,"name":"Architecture/data decisions","description":"**Requirements**\n\n* Determine the following and get green light from Ben on approach\n\n  * Decide on SDK (and which) or FF for limiting tracked users\n\n  * Data mapping for identifiers\n\n  * Data minimization/GDPR compliance\n\n  * Should user email be passed to Amplitude via user properties for debugging?\n\n  * Do we enable autocapture to start?\n","descriptionContentType":"TEXT","priority":null,"hasDeskTickets":false,"progress":0,"displayOrder":1999,"decimalDisplayOrder":1999,"crmDealIds":null,"tagIds":null,"tags":null,"updatedAt":"2026-05-12T19:05:37Z","updatedBy":610193,"deletedAt":null,"deletedBy":null,"parentTask":{"id":39861084,"type":"tasks"},"isPrivate":0,"lockdown":null,"status":"new","tasklist":{"id":2521973,"type":"tasklists"},"startDate":null,"dueDate":null,"startDateOffset":null,"dueDateOffset":null,"dueDateBase":null,"dueDateFromMilestone":false,"estimateMinutes":0,"accumulatedEstimatedMinutes":0,"assignees":[{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"commentFollowers":[{"id":490654,"type":"users"},{"id":610193,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"changeFollowers":[],"completeFollowers":[],"attachments":[],"notify":false,"isArchived":false,"capacities":null,"proofs":null,"userPermissions":{"canEdit":true,"canComplete":true,"canLogTime":false,"canViewEstTime":true,"canAddSubtasks":true},"createdBy":610193,"createdAt":"2026-03-17T20:57:55Z","sequence":null,"workflowStages":[{"workflowId":53311,"stageId":0,"stageTaskDisplayOrder":8660}],"dateUpdated":"2026-03-30T15:28:32Z","parentTaskId":39861084,"tasklistId":2521973,"assigneeUserIds":[643631],"assigneeUsers":[{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"assigneeCompanyIds":null,"assigneeCompanies":[],"assigneeTeamIds":null,"assigneeTeams":[],"assigneeJobRoleIds":null,"assigneeJobRoles":[],"createdByUserId":610193,"sequenceId":null},{"id":39861097,"name":"Add amplitude snippet to enable tracking","description":"**Requirements**\n\n* We should only implement amplitude tracking on production, and not on demo, qa or staging environments.\n\n* Make sure Amplitude is injected into all authenticated layouts that represent product usage.\n","descriptionContentType":"TEXT","priority":null,"hasDeskTickets":false,"progress":0,"displayOrder":2000,"decimalDisplayOrder":2000,"crmDealIds":null,"tagIds":null,"tags":null,"updatedAt":"2026-05-14T22:07:41Z","updatedBy":490645,"deletedAt":null,"deletedBy":null,"parentTask":{"id":39861084,"type":"tasks"},"isPrivate":0,"lockdown":null,"status":"new","tasklist":{"id":2521973,"type":"tasklists"},"startDate":null,"dueDate":null,"startDateOffset":null,"dueDateOffset":null,"dueDateBase":null,"dueDateFromMilestone":false,"estimateMinutes":0,"accumulatedEstimatedMinutes":0,"assignees":[{"id":645333,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"commentFollowers":[{"id":610193,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"},{"id":645330,"type":"users"}],"changeFollowers":[],"completeFollowers":[],"attachments":[],"notify":false,"isArchived":false,"capacities":null,"proofs":null,"userPermissions":{"canEdit":true,"canComplete":true,"canLogTime":false,"canViewEstTime":true,"canAddSubtasks":true},"createdBy":610193,"createdAt":"2026-03-17T20:08:37Z","sequence":null,"workflowStages":[{"workflowId":53311,"stageId":323586,"stageTaskDisplayOrder":2806}],"dateUpdated":"2026-05-14T22:06:46Z","parentTaskId":39861084,"tasklistId":2521973,"assigneeUserIds":[645333,643631],"assigneeUsers":[{"id":645333,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"assigneeCompanyIds":null,"assigneeCompanies":[],"assigneeTeamIds":null,"assigneeTeams":[],"assigneeJobRoleIds":null,"assigneeJobRoles":[],"createdByUserId":610193,"sequenceId":null},{"id":39861168,"name":"Utilize SDKs to limit what users are tracked in Amplitude","description":"**Background**\n\nIn order to keep our costs down, we cannot afford to track all users in Built.\n\nIf we do not limit the users we are tracking, our annual costs could go from $5k → $50k!\n\nAmplitude mentioned we could utilized their [SDK](https://amplitude.com/docs/sdks?mtl=GafVH1JmYdw)s to limit tracked users.\n\n**Requirements**\n\n* Roles: Only Company Admins, HR Admins, HR Managers, Limited Admins, Recruiting Admins, and Asset Admins\n\n  * We do not want to track users who aren’t assigned an admin role to start.\n\n* Modules/Plans: Only users who belong to companies subscribed to at least one of our modern modules - Org Design, Position Management, Succession Planning, Headcount Planning.\n\n  * We do not want to track users who belong to companies on legacy plans (PTO/TImesheets, Chart/Manage/Plan/Track Your Org)\n","descriptionContentType":"TEXT","priority":null,"hasDeskTickets":false,"progress":0,"displayOrder":2001,"decimalDisplayOrder":2001,"crmDealIds":null,"tagIds":null,"tags":null,"updatedAt":"2026-05-14T22:07:52Z","updatedBy":490645,"deletedAt":null,"deletedBy":null,"parentTask":{"id":39861084,"type":"tasks"},"isPrivate":0,"lockdown":null,"status":"new","tasklist":{"id":2521973,"type":"tasklists"},"startDate":null,"dueDate":null,"startDateOffset":null,"dueDateOffset":null,"dueDateBase":null,"dueDateFromMilestone":false,"estimateMinutes":0,"accumulatedEstimatedMinutes":0,"assignees":[{"id":645333,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"commentFollowers":[{"id":490654,"type":"users"},{"id":610193,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"},{"id":645330,"type":"users"}],"changeFollowers":[],"completeFollowers":[],"attachments":[],"notify":true,"isArchived":false,"capacities":null,"proofs":null,"userPermissions":{"canEdit":true,"canComplete":true,"canLogTime":false,"canViewEstTime":true,"canAddSubtasks":true},"createdBy":610193,"createdAt":"2026-03-17T20:15:06Z","sequence":null,"workflowStages":[{"workflowId":53311,"stageId":323586,"stageTaskDisplayOrder":2807}],"dateUpdated":"2026-05-14T22:06:49Z","parentTaskId":39861084,"tasklistId":2521973,"assigneeUserIds":[645333,643631],"assigneeUsers":[{"id":645333,"type":"users"}